The `definecurrency` command is not used to define a new node in the PBaaSChain. It's used to define a new currency. The nodes are actually defined in the PBaaSChain definition itself, as an array of objects with `networkaddress` and `nodeidentity` properties. For example:
```
"nodes": [
  {
    "networkaddress": "111.111.111.111:10000",
    "nodeidentity": "Node1@"
  },
  {
    "networkaddress": "111.111.111.112:10000",
    "nodeidentity": "Node2@"
  }
]
```
